   122‚Üí### Global methods ‚Ä¶
   156‚Üí## Variadic tuple patterns
   158‚ÜíWith TS-Pattern, you are now able to create array (or more accurately tuple) pattern with a variable number of elements:
   159‚Üí
   160‚Üí```ts
   161‚Üíconst example = (value: unknown) =>
      ‚Üí‚Ä¶
